es.ed0.tinyjson.parser

Class Token

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.ed0.tinyjson.parser.Token

  • public class Token
extends java.lang.Object
    Object representation of a token inside a json, this can be a text token (a string) a value token (numbers, booleans, etc) or a json (JSONObject and JSONArray).
    This object is only used during parsing and it cannot be retrieved from a generated JSONObject or JSONArray
